Deskero,is,a,brandable,customer,support,desk,that,comes,with,native,integrations,for,Twitter,Facebook,Google,LinkedIn,and,YouTube,It,uses,a,multi,channel,ticket,system,which,allows,Deskero,to,accept,tickets,from,a,wide,range,of,sources,Once,collected,tickets,can,be,organized,into,areas,or,groups,and,tagged,with,custom,labels,Deskero,also,enables,users,to,establish,a,knowledge,base,that,customers,can,browse,for,solutions,to,their,issues,Deskero,s,reporting,features,include,kinds,graphic,reports,users,can,create,custom,reports,if,they,prefer